metadata.name: Non Fungible Castle - VIP
metadata.description:
- Access to Interactive Cultural Experience at Nelahozeves Castle on Friday, November 4 with transport by historic train 
- Access to the Conference at the Lobkowicz Palace in Prague Castle on Saturday, November 5 
- Access to VIP Gala evening at the Lobkowicz Palace in Prague Castle on Saturday, November 5, with multi-course dinner menu and open bar with top-shelf spirits 
- Food, beverages (soft drinks, beer, wine), and entertainment included throughout entire program
- Exclusive NFT ticket with extended animation designed by Marek Ehrenberger and Martin Egrt
